description: Returns information about a trained model in a collaboration.

parameters.name: trainedModelArn
parameters.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the trained model that you want to return information about.

parameters.name: collaborationIdentifier
parameters.description: The collaboration ID that contains the trained model that you want to return information about.

nested_items.name: membershipIdentifier
nested_items.description: The membership ID of the member that created the trained model.

nested_items.name: collaborationIdentifier
nested_items.description: The collaboration ID of the collaboration that contains the trained model.

nested_items.name: trainedModelArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the trained model.

nested_items.name: name
nested_items.description: The name of the trained model.

nested_items.name: description
nested_items.description: The description of the trained model.

nested_items.name: status
nested_items.description: The status of the trained model.

nested_items.name: statusDetails
nested_items.description: Details about the status of a resource.

nested_items.name: statusCode
nested_items.description: The status code that was returned. The status code is intended for programmatic error handling. Clean Rooms ML will not change the status code for existing error conditions.

nested_items.name: message
nested_items.description: The error message that was returned. The message is intended for human consumption and can change at any time. Use the statusCode for programmatic error handling.

nested_items.name: configuredModelAlgorithmAssociationArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the configured model algorithm association that was used to create this trained model.

nested_items.name: resourceConfig
nested_items.description: The EC2 resource configuration that was used to train this model.

nested_items.name: instanceCount
nested_items.description: The number of resources that are used to train the model.

nested_items.name: instanceType
nested_items.description: The instance type that is used to train the model.

nested_items.name: volumeSizeInGB
nested_items.description: The maximum size of the instance that is used to train the model.

nested_items.name: stoppingCondition
nested_items.description: The stopping condition that determined when model training ended.

nested_items.name: maxRuntimeInSeconds
nested_items.description: The maximum amount of time, in seconds, that model training can run before it is terminated.

nested_items.name: metricsStatus
nested_items.description: The status of the model metrics.

nested_items.name: metricsStatusDetails
nested_items.description: Details about the status information for the model metrics.

nested_items.name: logsStatus
nested_items.description: Status information for the logs.

nested_items.name: logsStatusDetails
nested_items.description: Details about the status information for the logs.

nested_items.name: trainingContainerImageDigest
nested_items.description: Information about the training container image.

nested_items.name: createTime
nested_items.description: The time at which the trained model was created.

nested_items.name: updateTime
nested_items.description: The most recent time at which the trained model was updated.

nested_items.name: creatorAccountId
nested_items.description: The account ID of the member that created the trained model.
